# Cloud sync (optional). Copy to `.env.local` and fill in to turn sync ON.
# When these are absent, AJ Words stays 100% offline/local (the default) and the
# "Sync" button never appears.
#
# URL: Supabase → Settings → Data API (https://<project-ref>.supabase.co).
# Key: Supabase → Settings → API Keys → the "Publishable key" (sb_publishable_…),
# which is safe in the browser. The legacy anon JWT works here too.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-ref.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_YOUR-PUBLISHABLE-KEY
